"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/45435","Deputy Prime Minister","false","2014-04-01","<p> </p><p>The Government does not collect this data.</p><p> </p>","Tunbridge Wells","Greg Clark","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/45435/answer",,,,,,"2014-04-01T12:00:00.00Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/45435/answer","Biography information for Greg Clark","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/45435/answer",,,,,"58","Deputy Prime Minister","Deputy Prime Minister","2014-03-26","1","House of Commons","To ask the Deputy Prime Minister, with reference to the Answer of 19 June 2012, Official Report, columns 923-4W, on electoral register: fraud, how many successful prosecutions for electoral registration fraud there were in (a) 2012, (b) 2013 and (c) 2014 to date.","false","Biography information for Chris Ruane","Vale of Clwyd","Chris Ruane","194030"
